Package com.foreach.across.modules.entity.views.elements

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    CommonViewElements  
    ViewElement
    Simple interface representing a displayable value for an entity.
    ViewElementBuilder<T extends ViewElement>
    Base interface to create a single ViewElement instance.
    ViewElementBuilderFactory<T extends ViewElementBuilder>
    Creates a ViewElementBuilder that creates a specific ViewElement type.
    ViewElementBuilderFactoryAssembler
    All naming aside, this is the base interface for constructing a ViewElementBuilderFactory for a EntityPropertyDescriptor instance.
    ViewElementTypeLookupStrategy
    Strategy interface that looks up the most fitting ViewElement type to create.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CloningViewElementBuilderFactory<T extends ViewElementBuilder>
    Simple implementation of a ViewElementBuilderFactory that takes an instance of a ViewElementBuilder as a template, and when creating a builder will create a new instance and copy all bean properties from the template.

    ConversionServiceViewElement  
    ViewElementBuilderContext
    Represents the builder context in which ViewElement instances should be constructed.
    ViewElementBuilderSupport<T extends ViewElementSupport>  
    ViewElements

    ViewElementsHelper
    Utility object to help identifying ViewElement types.
